    Calendar cal = new Calendar();
    cal.SelectionMode = CalendarSelectionMode.SingleRange;
    cal.SelectedDates.AddRange(DateTime.Now.AddDays(-5), DateTime.Now);
 
when showing this calendar, you'll notice that the days are not selected.
 
 
Solution:
   Changes need to be made in SelectedDatesCollection.cs
 
In SelectedDatesCollection 2 methods are available: AddRange and AddRangeInternal.
The foreach loop of AddRange needs to be the same as the one from AddRangeInternal, this way at the end the last day added is set as SelectedDate, making the UI to update the selection.
 
 
